{Speech 38}{}{[Sobs and wipes his eyes] Well I'll be. Just imagine, she hadn't said a kind word to me since the day my mother died, and now this…And she wants to see me, I'd given up hope…[His face brightens] Listen, tell her, tell her that I … no, don't. Just say that I will definitely, you hear, definitely come to her! [Sighs] And that I love her…}
{Speech 38 Answer 39}{}{Of course, Vic, of course. Don't doubt it, I'll be sure to deliver it.}
