{Speech 40}{}{You do get into tight spots often, this will definitely come in handy for you. Look here, all the people I've met handle weapons, be it a pistol or a rifle, in a similar way, but there's one trick to it…}
{Speech 40 Answer 41}{}{Well I'll be, seems simple, but I'd never have figured it out myself. Thanks.}
